
Agenda:-
-------

Problem statement:-
-----------------
	Let's say your company is still in Java 5/6/7  and not ready to move to Java 8 quickly
		but they are expecting to avail java 1.8 New Date and Time API Features in the 
		existing project, How can you help them to achieve?

Solution 1:
----------
 	Try to use the Joda time artifact in your existing application

<dependency>
    <groupId>joda-time</groupId>
    <artifactId>joda-time</artifactId>
    <version>2.9.4</version>
</dependency>


Solution 2:
----------
 	Try to use the ThreeTen project artifact in your existing application
 	
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.threeten</groupId>
    <artifactId>threetenbp</artifactId>
    <version>1.3.1</version>
</dependency>


